Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,能见到你最后一面 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,休泰伊尔祭司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看来 好像不是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,裕司…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,火球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 结界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 解咒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像遇到麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是…敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是使者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是瓦尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是使者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是瓦尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,休泰伊尔 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,觉醒的人们啊 让使者见识你们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要…要打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,火球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,数量真多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,赐予我庞大力量的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦尔特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友啊 将这一幕烙印在你心中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 火球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 得救了 普莱德狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,身体吸收了龙之恩惠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,力量源源不绝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 抗魔法结界 抗物攻结界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟牠在里面等着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 火球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让你知道龙之力的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,普莱德狼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,微量攻击容易被闪躲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,火球 乱枪扫射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,速度真的很迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 火球 乱枪扫射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这点程度的魔法 休想伤我一根汗毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没效耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不只速度快 还很坚固
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,史莱姆 要不要试试那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 抗魔法结界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,强化魔力 强化物攻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让你见识本大爷的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了 看起来就像暂停一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 火球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,盖格尔的魔兽防具 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 火球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是复原他的伤势 还能强化能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 火球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,恢复的速度真快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,龙之恩惠的诅咒真强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 既然是诅咒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,普莱德狼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,火球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 火球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就说了没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 极解咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子进行得很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抗物攻结界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,结界要破掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,裕司 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 魔力撒网
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 魔力撒网 x 10
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,极灭业火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,时机到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不论是我想打倒使者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还是使者想打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,结果都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我将我与追随者的命都奉献给您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,恳请您如神谕所示…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,比我预期得好解决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦尔特临死前说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如神谕所示…"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,难道 那道神谕…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力被吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,愿此肮脏的世界获得救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的光芒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉有点不妙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,吾乃… 贤者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,吾乃贤者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他是瓦尔特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我告诉你的神谕还有后续
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,引导者之死 贤者降临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我死后 你会以贤者的身份降临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,并且拯救这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓的"引导者之死" 是指"瓦尔特的死"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 贤者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,神话书籍里 是这样写的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,远古时 有位勇于讨伐真龙的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因不敌真龙之力 死于非命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦尔特 可能是为了复活他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,以自身和信众的性命作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,进行类似"神灵召唤"的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,神灵召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得这是召唤神的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是… 他是"神"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他才不是我们的"神"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不可能是"神"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,终焉业火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,跟裕司的好像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,二话不说就使用终焉业火…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,体力增强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,移动强化 防御力强化 跳跃强化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样应该能方便战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好 要上啰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 对物攻结界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 火球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,极灭业火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 散开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 对物攻结界 x 10
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法传送 火球 乱枪扫射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,极灭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,魔兽隐形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,…业火
